*$ Plot Library Routines for POSTMORTEM
*  -------------------------------------
C
C   Original Version N.P. Rees
C
C   01/06/89, PA:  Plot_mode switch installed for multiple plots
C   23/08/89, PA:  Plot_scale_type installed for auto-scaling/fixed
C                  range plots.  Phase plot range now fixed.
C   06/09/89, PA:  Plot_prompt switch determines whether the default
C                  plot device is used or the device is always prompted
C                  for.
C   15/09/89, PA:  Plot of AMP/PHASE or COS/SIN now controlled only
C                  by SET-DISPLAY-OPTION sub-option and not by prompt.
C   14/11/89, PA:  Plot_mode option requesting "Brief" output installed.
C   10/10/90, PA:  Plot_fit option added and support for plotting fits
C                  to spacing data for phase.
C   13/1/92, DJT:  Plot_zeros option added to allow plotting of zero data
C                  values (these are ignored as bad data by default).
C
